<!-- ##### SECTION Short_Description ##### -->

Functions to retrieve monitors information in Xinerama mode

<!-- ##### SECTION Long_Description ##### -->
<para>

This section describes the functions available to retrieve information
about the monitors size and positioning when an application is started
on virtual screen (e.g. Xinerama mode on X).

